38:33.354 --> 38:34.834
♪ What have I done?

38:34.877 --> 38:36.096
What are you doing?

38:36.139 --> 38:39.273
Uh, I am...
paying you back.

38:39.317 --> 38:40.927
By going
with booties again?

38:40.970 --> 38:42.537
I am disappointed.

38:42.581 --> 38:44.060
I thought
you were more original.

38:44.104 --> 38:45.932
It has been
a busy couple of days.

38:45.975 --> 38:49.718
Plus I -- I accidentally
ordered twice, so...

38:49.762 --> 38:51.024
You're welcome.

38:51.067 --> 38:52.982
♪ Ready to overload

38:53.026 --> 38:56.421
Okay. I'm gonna go,
leave you to it.

38:56.464 --> 38:58.379
Hey, um...

38:58.423 --> 38:59.989
[ Chuckles ] Yeah?

39:00.033 --> 39:02.122
♪ Even when you tell lies,
tell lies ♪

39:02.165 --> 39:04.516
You and Nolan --

39:04.559 --> 39:06.082
you did good work today.

39:06.126 --> 39:08.955
♪ You tell lies, tell lies

39:08.998 --> 39:10.217
I've been told
that it's important

39:10.260 --> 39:12.306
for a supervisor
to give praise.

39:12.350 --> 39:14.221
Oh.

39:14.264 --> 39:16.528
Well, thank you.

39:16.571 --> 39:18.356
What else do you appreciate
about me?

39:18.399 --> 39:20.401
That you know
when not to push your luck.

39:20.445 --> 39:22.316
Yes. Okay. Good night.

39:22.360 --> 39:23.404
Good night.
Good night.

