39:29.802 --> 39:31.456
Why isn't it on vibrate?
Go! Go! Go! Go!

39:31.499 --> 39:32.805
It's gonna wake him up.
It's gonna wake him up.

39:32.848 --> 39:34.546
Don't wake up, don't wake up,
don't wake up.

39:34.589 --> 39:38.811
♪ I'll be here for you,
for years to come ♪

39:38.854 --> 39:41.422
[ Both sigh heavily ]

39:41.466 --> 39:42.902
Thank God.

39:42.945 --> 39:45.383
Yes!
They caught Claire Ivey!

39:45.426 --> 39:46.514
[ Jack crying ]

39:46.558 --> 39:49.952
♪ For years to come [ Sighs ]

39:49.996 --> 39:51.780
♪ You-ou-ou

39:51.824 --> 39:52.651
♪ You-ou-ou-ou-ou

39:52.694 --> 39:54.435
You still love me, right?

39:54.479 --> 39:56.437
♪♪

39:56.481 --> 39:59.135
♪ No matter the distance,
wherever you are ♪

39:59.179 --> 40:01.094
[ Furniture scraping ]

40:01.137 --> 40:03.401
Tamara? Do you need help?

40:03.444 --> 40:05.577
Tamara: Nope.[ Chuckling ] Okay.

40:05.620 --> 40:07.666
[ Scraping continues ]

40:07.709 --> 40:10.146
♪♪

40:10.190 --> 40:12.627
♪ And I'll be here for you

40:12.671 --> 40:14.629
Are you sure?

40:14.673 --> 40:16.762
Okay, I'm done.

40:16.805 --> 40:18.241
Promise me
you won't be mad.

40:18.285 --> 40:20.461
Of course. I-I promise.

40:20.505 --> 40:22.463
Okay. Uh...

40:22.507 --> 40:26.511
♪ I'll be here for you,
for years to come ♪

40:26.554 --> 40:28.774
♪ You-ou-ou

40:28.817 --> 40:31.907
♪ You-ou-ou-ou-ou

40:31.951 --> 40:33.996
♪ I'll be here for you...

40:34.040 --> 40:35.520
Do you like it?

40:35.563 --> 40:36.782
Uh...

40:36.825 --> 40:37.913
[ Exhales sharply ]

40:37.957 --> 40:40.002
No. I...

40:40.046 --> 40:41.221
I love it.

40:41.264 --> 40:43.963
♪ Even in death,
I hope you always know ♪

40:44.006 --> 40:46.487
♪ That I was here for you

40:46.531 --> 40:49.055
♪♪

40:49.098 --> 40:53.320
♪ And I'll be here for you,
for years to come ♪

40:53.363 --> 40:56.541
I know breaking up over text
isn't super mature.

40:56.584 --> 40:58.238
No. It's -- It's fine.

40:58.281 --> 41:00.414
I-I just wanted to make sure
it wasn't something I did.

41:00.458 --> 41:02.677
It's not you.
I-I know that's a cliché,

41:02.721 --> 41:03.809
but I-I really mean it.

41:03.852 --> 41:05.941
You're -- You're great.

41:05.985 --> 41:08.814
You're funny and handsome.

41:08.857 --> 41:10.555
Warm. Smart.

41:10.598 --> 41:12.687
Confused.

41:12.731 --> 41:15.298
It's just --
I'm good at a lotta things.

41:15.342 --> 41:18.040
But I am terrible
at relationships.

41:18.084 --> 41:20.347
And they all go
the same way.

41:20.390 --> 41:22.262
We'll start dating.
You'll open up.

41:22.305 --> 41:23.698
I'll distract you
with jokes

41:23.742 --> 41:25.744
so you don't notice
that I'm keeping you away,

41:25.787 --> 41:27.223
until you get tired
of my bull

41:27.267 --> 41:29.095
and you tell me
this one-sided relationship

41:29.138 --> 41:30.879
isn't working
and I'll tell you,

41:30.923 --> 41:33.665
"Well, this is who I am,
take it or leave it."

41:33.708 --> 41:35.275
And you'll leave it.

41:35.318 --> 41:38.234
So, you know,
I thought I'd skip to the end.

41:38.278 --> 41:40.410
Wow.

41:40.454 --> 41:41.586
That sounds like a lot.

41:41.629 --> 41:43.588
Well, that's me.
I'm a lot.

41:43.631 --> 41:45.285
Yeah, thing is,
I-I'm not believing it.

41:45.328 --> 41:47.156
I mean, that you're bad
at relationships --

41:47.200 --> 41:49.071
totally believable.

41:49.115 --> 41:51.291
By your own admission,
you've never --

41:51.334 --> 41:53.859
never actually been in one.
Which is fine.

41:53.902 --> 41:57.906
But I am standing here as living
proof that people can change.

41:57.950 --> 42:00.430
Who you were
up until this very moment

42:00.474 --> 42:03.216
is not who you have to be
moving forward.

42:03.259 --> 42:05.871
So, really,
the question here is:

42:05.914 --> 42:08.700
Do I make you want to show up
differently?

42:08.743 --> 42:13.835
And...so that you know,
if you say that I do...

42:13.879 --> 42:15.358
I'm all in.

42:15.402 --> 42:17.317
Well...

42:17.360 --> 42:19.449
when you put it that way.

42:19.493 --> 42:22.670
♪ I'll be here for you,
for years to come ♪

